================================================================================
IMPORTANT: NON-COMMERCIAL RESEARCH DEMO
================================================================================

This application is a NON-COMMERCIAL research demonstration. It does not
redistribute any model weights; weights are downloaded at runtime, on the
Hugging Face Space, directly from their respective upstream repositories.

The application wraps `facebook/tribev2` and, transitively, several
foundation models. Each carries its own license, and the most restrictive
of these governs how the *combined* system may be used. The TRIBE v2
weights are released under a NON-COMMERCIAL license; therefore this demo,
and any use of its predictions, is restricted to non-commercial research
and evaluation purposes.

